SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(distinct(CMON_MONTHNUMBER)) from :1/CMON where exists (select CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO from :1/CLNT where :2 and CLNT101_ADMNO = CMON_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CMON_CLNTNO) and CMON_MONTHNUMBER between :3 and :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5' for fetch only
